00:42:12.113 --> 00:42:14.032 position:25.24%,start align:start size:57.62% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>We just want to get home.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1159
00:42:21.914 --> 00:42:24.167 position:19.52%,start align:start size:69.05% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Tuvok, release the force-field.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

