00:42:25.877 --> 00:42:27.795 position:42.38%,start align:start size:25.24% line:73.96% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Captain.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1161
00:42:25.877 --> 00:42:27.795 position:44.29%,start align:start size:21.43% line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Do it.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

